What is your current employment status?

Note that for purposes of this study full time is considered to be working at least 40 hours per week. Less than 40 hours of work per week is considered part time.
Q2.4:
What is your current employment type?

Note that for the purposes of this study blue collar work can be generally considered as working primarily with your hands or through physical activity, while white collar work can be considered working primarily without physical activity or in clerical/administrative roles.
